Package structures.trees

Class SelfBalancingTree<K extends java.lang.Comparable,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.trees.BinarySearchTree<K,V>
      • structures.trees.SelfBalancingTree<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Generic type for keys. Must be comparable
    V - Generic type for values.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<K>, DataStructure<K>, BinaryTree<K,V>

    public abstract class SelfBalancingTree<K extends java.lang.Comparable,V>
extends BinarySearchTree<K,V>
    Abstract class for Self balancing trees such as AVLTree and Red Black Tree. The rotation function are implemented in this class as they are used by both types of trees.
